frames.caption: A group of hooded figures approaches a massive, ancient stone portal in a desolate desert landscape. Red lightning crackles dramatically from the portal, illuminating the scene with an eerie glow. The sky is overcast, adding to the ominous atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a barren desert with a group of cloaked individuals walking towards a large, intricately carved stone portal. The portal emits red lightning, creating a supernatural and foreboding ambiance.

frames.caption: A group of hooded figures in dark robes approaches a massive, ancient stone portal. A striking red lightning bolt descends from the stormy sky, illuminating the scene with an eerie glow. The atmosphere is mysterious and foreboding, as the figures move towards the ominous gateway.
frames.description: The scene is set in a desolate desert landscape under a stormy sky. A monumental stone portal stands at the center, with intricate carvings and symbols. Hooded figures walk towards the portal as a red lightning bolt dramatically strikes down from above.

frames.caption: A group of hooded figures approaches a massive, ancient stone gate emitting a bright red light. Lightning strikes dramatically from the sky, connecting with the gate, creating an intense and mystical atmosphere. The scene is set in a desolate, sandy landscape under a cloudy sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mysterious and dramatic setting where hooded figures are drawn towards a monumental stone gate. The environment is otherworldly, with a striking red lightning bolt connecting the sky to the gate, suggesting a ritualistic or supernatural event.
